| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4454 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d92cfa27-3459-587e-b8d5-e94d9b7649ba"
